# ─── MindPulse Blog — API Configuration ───────────────────────────────────────
# Set ONE of these. NVIDIA is recommended (free, no card required).

# ✅ OPTION 1: NVIDIA Build — FREE (Llama 4 Maverick)
# Get your key at: https://build.nvidia.com → any model → "Get API Key"
NVIDIA_API_KEY=your_nvidia_api_key_here

# ─── Alternative providers (comment out NVIDIA_API_KEY to use these) ───────────

# OPTION 2: Google Gemini — Free tier available
# Get key: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
# GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_google_api_key_here

# OPTION 3: Groq — Free and very fast
# Get key: https://console.groq.com/keys
# GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here

# OPTION 4: OpenAI — Paid
# OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here
